    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but therapy and self-care... that's just more stuff to try and fail at. it's like trying to patch a sinking ship with Scotch tape. i've done the whole \"work on yourself\" thing so many times and the loop just resets. it's not a loop i can walk out of. i feel like i'm just starring in a tragedy that wont end.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
